{
  "id": "adv_main_01_10_06",
  "title": "星見編2章40話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_backstage-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "はぁっ……はぁっ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*huff* *huff*",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "…………ふぅ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.162086176872254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（緊張。集中。そんな空気が充満しているな）\n（だが、不思議と重く感じない。むしろ心地良い）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Tension. Focus. The air is filled with it.)\n(But‚ strangely enough‚ it doesn’t weigh heavily on me. If anything‚ it feels good.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.212086164951325,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（NEXT VENUSグランプリ）\n（――その予選が、いよいよ始まるんだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(could climb to the top in live concert battles.)\n(The preliminary round is about to start.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.278752831617993,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}、ちょっといいか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ {user}‚ got a minute?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.811383052666983,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 20.811383052666947
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 23.044716386000317
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 23.044716386000317
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "実はな、NEXT VENUSグランプリの運営から",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s like this‚ the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix management",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.211383052666992,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "少し手伝ってくれないかという依頼が来てな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "sent a request asking if I could help them with something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.74471638600032,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……どうするんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you going to do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.08582753737768,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……行こうと思う。ただそうなると",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think I’ll go. But if I do‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.45249420404435,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "俺は事務所のグループのマネジメントは出来ない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won’t be able to manage any of our agency’s groups.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.48582753737768,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "俺に両方見ろってことですよね\nやります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you want me to look after both groups?\nI’ll do it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.37832686378245,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そう言うと思った",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought you’d say that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.47832686378245,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ずっと気になっていたんです。もう少しうまくやれば\n両方を見ることが出来たんじゃないかって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s been on my mind a lot. What if I’d managed things better?\nI might’ve been able to look after both groups.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.19499355429098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……分かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Okay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.994993554290986,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "三枝信司",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shinji",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "じゃあ後は、自分の口からみんなに伝えるんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ now you just have to deliver the news to everyone yourself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.76166022095766,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 61.494993554290986
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（三枝さん、初めからそのつもりだったのかもな）\n（よし、気合を入れ直して……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(This might have been Mr. Saegusa’s plan all along.)\n(Alright‚ time to re-motivate myself…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.9283268876243,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_lesson-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 69.39499355429099
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "えーー、さて……\nみんな、本日も練習お疲れ様でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ everyone…\nYou all did a great job at practice today!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.99110877032864,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "なんですの？　その改まった態度は\n緊張してるんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s this? Why the stiff and formal attitude?\nAre you nervous?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.99110877032865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "なになに？　何かあったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ooh! Did something happen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.59110877032865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "も、もしかして……辞めるとか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "D-don’t tell us you’re quitting?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.35997507091153,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "まさか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ no…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.45185706134427,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "結婚……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Marriage…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.05185706134428,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "エーーーーっ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whaaat?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.65185706134427,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "違う違う！　勝手に話を膨らませないでくれ\n……まず最初に、みんなに報告がある――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ no‚ no! Please don’t go jumping to conclusions!\nFirst‚ I have an announcement for you all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.15185706134432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（意外にも、俺の報告への反対意見はなかった）\n（三枝さんはみんなの気持ちを理解していたらしい）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Surprisingly‚ nobody was opposed to the news I gave them.)\n(I guess Mr. Saegusa got a good reading on how they all felt.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.51852372801092,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "――さて、みんなも知っている通り、来週\nNEXT VENUSグランプリの予選が開かれる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ as you all know‚ next week‚\nthe NEXT VENUS Grand Prix preliminary round will begin.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.3601107946613,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "正直、予選を突破するのも難しいんじゃないか……\nそう思ったこともあったけど、今は違う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To be honest‚ I always thought making it through the preliminary round would be quite difficult.\nBut I don’t think that way anymore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.02677746132797,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "デビュー間もない新人で、ここまでのパフォーマンスが\n出来るグループは滅多にいない。自信を持っていい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re all newcomers who’ve just barely made their debut‚ yet your performances are so polished.\nNot many other groups are like you. So I think we can be confident.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.46702299974486,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "当たり前です\n私がいるんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course we can be confident.\nI’m on the team.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.14882520896325,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんもね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And Kotono‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.94882520896329,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "……違う\n全員よ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No.\nIt’s all of us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.81726063948997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "……うん、だよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… you’re right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.9342901394976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_06/sud_vo_adv_main_01_10_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "緊張もするだろうし、不安にもなるだろうと思う\nけど、自分の精一杯の力を出せるように集中しよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think you’ll get nervous‚ and you’ll probably also feel uneasy.\nBut just focus on giving your personal best performance.",
